{"tid":1894121,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"知唔知道點解以加一定要幫襯黃店！","createTime":"2020-02-23T17:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T09:37:53.000Z","uid":326261,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc00a3c70fcf1c5f4f82b3540192f1bb81bc49b","tid":1894121,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:07:48.000Z","msg":"好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為要自保呀！<br />\n我都知會有人問有咩關系<br />\n緊係有la dllm<br />\n你諗下目前為止賴親嘢既係咩人？<br />\n係大陸人同藍絲（因為佢嘅會返大陸或者同大陸人接觸）<br />\n而佢哋係絕對唔會幫襯龍門之類嘅鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />簡單啲來講就係黃店本身已經擁有一個過濾嘅能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過濾到帶菌者嘅機會極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相信反其他立場不知名嘅鋪頭真係唔知有咩人去過㗎<br />\n講到咁你都唔明或者唔行動<br />\n瀨咗嘢就唔好問點解啦"},{"pid":"6ac33eb5e626adabebd06cfc1c55028975462a5a","tid":1894121,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:08:17.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"a766b0503457b442d92ec31581a0d8228dd637e9","tid":1894121,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"5269f0e4a24c40f3bb717e328ac6cec104be7a7f","tid":1894121,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:19:36.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"fc378bd39c65dfb4db7798146d0ddf88df8e9b19","tid":1894121,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:47:28.000Z","msg":"係美國冇得幫襯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9700ced4beb8befa30b08c71ddea79d4e715a38c","tid":1894121,"uid":250439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T03:00:23.000Z","msg":"721 831 101 1111"},{"pid":"6cc17a70d1279836cc6dcf5d94136e2b5658a74f","tid":1894121,"uid":101906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T03:01:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc9f070b56f299ccf40ccef314c114c2d8cc8600","tid":189